'''Leonardo Sierra Monteiro''' (born [[February 3]], 1987), better known as '''Leonardo Monteiro''', is a [[Brazilian people|Brazilian]] actor,<ref>{{cite web|title=Apresentadores da TV CRUJ se reunem 12 anos apos o fim do programa|url=http://revistaquem.globo.com/Popquem/noticia/2015/10/apresentadores-da-tv-cruj-se-reunem-12-anos-apos-o-fim-do-programa.html|work=Revista Quem|language=Brazilian Portuguese|accessdate=February 28, 2017}}</ref> [[engineer]] and [[entrepreneur]] that was known nationally as an actor when he was a child, making his debut in Brazilian version of [[Disney Club]] in 1997, which later became [[Disney CRUJ]]<ref>{{cite interview|title=TV Cruj interrompe a transmissão do SBT durante o The Noite|url=http://www.sbt.com.br/thenoite/fiquepordentro/69607/TV-Cruj-interrompe-a-transmissao-do-SBT-durante-o-The-Noite.html|interviewer=[[Danilo Gentili]]|work=[[The Noite com Danilo Gentili]]|date=October 12, 2015|accessdate=February 28, 2017}}</ref> and in 2013 started a [[startup company|startup]] of price intelligence in physical retail called [[InfoPrice]], that in 2015 part has acquired by [[B2W]] an online retail company in Latin America.<ref>{{cite web|title=Descubra quem é a InfoPrice e como ela pode ajudar o seu negócio|url=http://blog.infopricesa.com.br/como-infoprice-ajuda-seu-negocio/}}</ref>

